('192d47c5-cb0e-4692-a2d8-57ea072b2a1d', 'a3000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Áo sơ mi cao cấp - New Cotton Shirt and pant', 'new-cotton-shirt-and-pant-15', 'Very nice and attractive (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 27500000.0, 'active', 4.5, 10),
('915ec4af-7105-40b0-8c8b-bc11218f0dfb', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Futuristic Holographic Soccer Cleats', 'futuristic-holographic-soccer-cleats-16', 'Step onto the field and stand out from the crowd with these eye-catching holographic soccer cleats. Designed for the modern player, these cleats feature a sleek silhouette, lightweight construction for maximum agility, and durable studs for optimal traction. The shimmering holographic finish reflects a rainbow of colors as you move, ensuring that you''ll be noticed for both your skills and style. Perfect for the fashion-forward athlete who wants to make a statement. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 975000.0, 'active', 4.5, 10),
('c68dca78-9048-452d-9b70-bf500272fd41', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Rainbow Glitter High Heels', 'rainbow-glitter-high-heels-17', 'Step into the spotlight with these eye-catching rainbow glitter high heels. Designed to dazzle, each shoe boasts a kaleidoscope of shimmering colors that catch and reflect light with every step. Perfect for special occasions or a night out, these stunners are sure to turn heads and elevate any ensemble. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 975000.0, 'active', 4.5, 34),
('643ff661-6963-4396-bba3-673fb8ecadb0', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Giày sneaker thể thao - Vibrant Runners: Bold Orange & Blue Sneakers', 'vibrant-runners-bold-orange-blue-sneakers-18', 'Step into style with these eye-catching sneakers featuring a striking combination of orange and blue hues. Designed for both comfort and fashion, these shoes come with flexible soles and cushioned insoles, perfect for active individuals who don''t compromise on style. The reflective silver accents add a touch of modernity, making them a standout accessory for your workout or casual wear. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 675000.0, 'active', 4.5, 58),
('47addff2-4d99-4935-b1d4-6fee9e879d1f', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Futuristic Silver and Gold High-Top Sneaker', 'futuristic-silver-and-gold-high-top-sneaker-19', 'Step into the future with this eye-catching high-top sneaker, designed for those who dare to stand out. The sneaker features a sleek silver body with striking gold accents, offering a modern twist on classic footwear. Its high-top design provides support and style, making it the perfect addition to any avant-garde fashion collection. Grab a pair today and elevate your shoe game! (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 1700000.0, 'active', 4.5, 82),
('7041f213-2c7d-43d6-baf3-926b51619756', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Elegant Patent Leather Peep-Toe Pumps with Gold-Tone Heel', 'elegant-patent-leather-peep-toe-pumps-20', 'Step into sophistication with these chic peep-toe pumps, showcasing a lustrous patent leather finish and an eye-catching gold-tone block heel. The ornate buckle detail adds a touch of glamour, perfect for elevating your evening attire or complementing a polished daytime look. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 1325000.0, 'active', 4.5, 106),
('3a139b37-07ed-4d82-91fa-60b60e7e2dfa', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Elegant Purple Leather Loafers', 'elegant-purple-leather-loafers-21', 'Step into sophistication with our Elegant Purple Leather Loafers, perfect for making a bold statement. Crafted from high-quality leather with a vibrant purple finish, these shoes feature a classic loafer silhouette that''s been updated with a contemporary twist. The comfortable slip-on design and durable soles ensure both style and functionality for the modern man. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 425000.0, 'active', 4.5, 130),
('45b247ee-b30b-43ee-81e3-0e25d54e469b', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Giày thời trang - Classic Blue Suede Casual Shoes', 'classic-blue-suede-casual-shoes-22', 'Step into comfort with our Classic Blue Suede Casual Shoes, perfect for everyday wear. These shoes feature a stylish blue suede upper, durable rubber soles for superior traction, and classic lace-up fronts for a snug fit. The sleek design pairs well with both jeans and chinos, making them a versatile addition to any wardrobe. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 975000.0, 'active', 4.5, 154),
('ec763341-122e-43b1-9531-6b74e0f046e1', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Giày thời trang - Broken white Bandung Shoes', 'broken-white-bandung-shoes-23', 'Sepatu Warna broken white produk lokal produksi bandung (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 1500000.0, 'active', 4.5, 178),
('d1772944-eb8b-46a0-ab8a-1947be933a53', 'c1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Giày sneaker thể thao - Sneakers Saba Veloz Low Black White', 'sneakers-saba-veloz-low-black-white-24', 'Sepatu Vulcaniized dari bahan kanvas merk SABA, dengan kualitas yang premium sangat nyaman dipakai (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 1000000.0, 'active', 4.5, 202),
('efa608c9-d77f-474b-989c-8a6b7f8f2f47', 'c2000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Sandal quai ngang - Chic Summer Denim Espadrille Sandals', 'chic-summer-denim-espadrille-sandals-25', 'Step into summer with style in our denim espadrille sandals. Featuring a braided jute sole for a classic touch and adjustable denim straps for a snug fit, these sandals offer both comfort and a fashionable edge. The easy slip-on design ensures convenience for beach days or casual outings. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 825000.0, 'active', 4.5, 10),
('6c14b92f-6052-43a7-9e6d-927443e16865', 'c3000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Giày boots cá tính - Futuristic Chic High-Heel Boots', 'futuristic-chic-high-heel-boots-26', 'Elevate your style with our cutting-edge high-heel boots that blend bold design with avant-garde aesthetics. These boots feature a unique color-block heel, a sleek silhouette, and a versatile light grey finish that pairs easily with any cutting-edge outfit. Crafted for the fashion-forward individual, these boots are sure to make a statement. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 900000.0, 'active', 4.5, 10),
('eb638ed7-6a23-4e6d-ac8f-7360991c4ee6', 'd1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', 'Túi xách cao cấp - Chic Transparent Fashion Handbag', 'chic-transparent-fashion-handbag-27', 'Elevate your style with our Chic Transparent Fashion Handbag, perfect for showcasing your essentials with a clear, modern edge. This trendy accessory features durable acrylic construction, luxe gold-tone hardware, and an elegant chain strap. Its compact size ensures you can carry your day-to-day items with ease and sophistication. (Sản phẩm nhập khẩu chính hãng chất lượng cao, phân phối độc quyền bởi Shofy Fashion).', 1525000.0, 'active', 4.5, 10);
